Total Continues Talks With Potential Buyer for Lindsey Refinery

-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 
2011-09-27T08:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/total-continues-talks-with-potential-buyer-for-lindsey-refinery.html
Total SA (FP) ,  Europe ’s third-largest
oil producer, is continuing talks with a potential buyer for the
sale of its Lindsey refinery in the U.K.  “It’s not easy to sell a refinery in Europe these days,”
Patrice de Vivies, senior vice president for Northern Europe at
Total, said in Aberdeen, Scotland. “It will take some time.”  The company is hoping to sell the refinery by the end of
the year, Chief Financial Officer Patrick de la Chevardiere said
July 29.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduard Gismatullin in London at 
